company_name: FRIEDRICH FRESE TABAKWAREN GROSSHANDLUNG NACHFOLGERIN CHRISTINE NUYKEN
information: The company FRIEDRICH FRESE TABAKWAREN GROSSHANDLUNG NACHFOLGERIN CHRISTINE NUYKEN, is a Wholesaler, founded in 1946, which operates in the Tobacco and smokers items industry. It also operates in the Tobacco industries. It is based in Oberhausen, Germany.
